                                           IGraph graph)
                                    throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        Description copied from interface: ITSP
        Find a solution to the TSP problem, for the graph passed by argument, before the time limit expires. The solution returned begins by the first edge stored in the graph.
        Specified by:
        computeSolution in interface ITSP
        Parameters:
        timeLimit - The limit of time, in ms.
        graph - The graph to analyse.
        Returns:
        Array with the solutions : the value at the index "i" is the index of the previous node.
        Throws:
        java.lang.InterruptedException - Throws the exception in case of interruption.
